
PRIEST
!
Maximum HP: 150
Damage: 15
One who has devoted her life to God.
She is able to manifest the power of God through the strength of her faith.

Skills
- Light Ray: Emits a radiant beam of divine energy, damaging enemies.
- Holy Smite: Strikes enemies with a powerful, holy attack.
- Wait and See: Takes a moment to assess the situation before making a move.
!


KNIGHT
@
Maximum HP: 250
Damage: 8
A Knight that has tempered his body and relies on weapons.
This is the most common job amongst adventurers.

Skills:
- Slash: Executes a standard slashing attack with the weapon.
- Dual Slash: Performs two quick slashes in succession.
- Wait and See: Pauses to evaluate the battlefield before acting.
@


MAGE
#
Maximum HP: 150
Damage: 7
A mage that fights by using the knowledge of spells and the power of his mind.
He is unskilled in hand-to-hand combat, but is able to shield himself for defense.

Skills:
- Fireball: Casts a fiery projectile at enemies.
- Lightning Bolt: Unleashes a bolt of lightning to strike foes.
- Wait and See: Takes a moment to strategize and plan the next magical action.
#


SCORPION
$
Maximum HP: 100
Damage: 20
A scorpion that was enlarged in an experiment to be bigger than a human.

Skills:
- Poison Sting: Injects venom into enemies, causing severe damage.
- Wait and See: Observes the surroundings before deciding on the next move.
$


SUICIDE ROCK
%
Maximum HP: 100
Damage: 20
A magical rock creature that gets excited and explodes.
It seems as though it was developed for war.

Skills:
- Self Destruct: Sacrifices itself to cause a powerful explosion.
- Throw Rock: Hurls a large rock at enemies.
- Wait and See: A moment of anticipation before taking any action.
%


SKELETON
^
Maximum HP: 80
Damage: 20
Even though its flesh has completely rotted away and all that remains is bone, it is able to move due to a curse.

Skills:
- Stab: Strikes with a bony weapon (0w<).
- Heal: Uses dark magic to restore its own health.
- Wait and See: Takes a moment to assess the battlefield.
^


DARK STALKER
&
Maximum HP: 100
Damage: 15
It hides in the shadows, taking the lives of those who oppose the Ancient King.

Skills:
- Dark Slash: Executes a swift, shadow-infused slashing attack.
- Triple Slash: Performs a series of three quick slashes.
- Wait and See: Lurks in the shadows, observing before making a move.
&


ANCIENT BISHOP
*
Maximum HP: 100
Damage: 15
Ones who adhere to the most ancient religion even now.

Skills:
- Holy Sword: Summons a sacred sword to strike down enemies.
- Heal: Calls upon divine energy to restore health.
- Wait and See: Takes a moment to contemplate the divine plan before acting.
*